   <p><img class="thumbleft" src="/sites/foodservices.appstate.edu/files/Pizzeria_0.jpg" alt="the pizzeria logo" width="285" height="90" />In&nbsp;Sanford Commons in the Roess Dining Hall</p><p><strong>The Pizzeria</strong> offers freshly prepared pizza, by the slice or by the pie. Sample classic pepperoni or veggie or try one of the specialty pies â€“ Hawaiian, Steak and Cheese and more. And, we will deliver, too! Call 828-262-2101 to place an order for pick-up or delivery!</p><p><strong>*The menu may vary due to changes in production and/or product availability.*</strong></p><h3>Hours</h3><p>Monday - Friday: 10:30 am - 10:30 pm<br />Saturday - Sunday:&nbsp; 11:00 am - 10:30 pm</p><h3>Delivery Hours</h3><p>Sunday - Friday: 4:30 pm - 11:00 pm<br />Closed Saturday<br /><em><strong><br />Call 828-262-2101 to order</strong></em></p><h3>Menu</h3><p>(L): Local (GF): Gluten Friendly (V): Vegetarian (V+): Vegan</p><table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1"><tbody><tr><td class="rtecenter" colspan="4" align="center"><strong>Specialty Pizzas <strong>(12" or 16")</strong><br /></strong></td></tr><tr><td colspan="4" width="50%"><p><strong><strong></strong></strong> <strong>Bacon &amp; Cheddar</strong><br />Bacon, cheddar, marinara and more cheddar.</p><p><strong>Chicken Bacon Ranch</strong><br />Garlic butter base with ranch-marinated chicken, bacon, oregano and a ranch dressing drizzle.</p><p><strong>Hawaiian</strong><br />Ham and pineapple.&nbsp; Simple and delicious.</p><p><strong>Hot Wing</strong><br />Hot sauce base with marinated chicken, cheese and a ranch dressing drizzle.</p><p><strong>Meat Lovers</strong><br />All your favorites - pepperoni, ham, beef, sausage and bacon.</p><p><strong>Steak &amp; Cheese</strong><br />Steak and piles of cheese with a steak sauce drizzle.</p><p><strong>Supreme</strong><br />Pepperoni, sausage, beef, green peppers, onions, mushrooms and black olives.</p><p><strong>Veggie</strong><br />Veggie heaven - green peppers, onions, mushrooms, black olives and tomatoes.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="rtecenter" colspan="4" align="center"><strong>Build Your Own Whole Pizza (12" or 16")<br /></strong><em>Mix and match to make your own pizza masterpiece - custom made to order and priced by the topping</em><strong><br /></strong></td></tr><tr><td align="center"><strong>Meats &amp; Cheese<br /> </strong></td><td align="center"><strong>Veggies (V+)<br /></strong></td><td align="center"><strong>Extras<br /></strong></td><td align="center"><strong>Additional Selections<br /></strong></td></tr><tr><td class="rteleft" width="25%">Bacon<br />Beef<br />Chicken<br />Ham<br />Pepperoni<br />Pork<br />Mozzarella Cheese (V)</td><td width="25%">Black Olives<br />Green Peppers<br />Mushrooms<br />Onions<br />Pineapple<br />Tomatoes</td><td width="25%">Extra Cheese<br />Extra Pepperoni<br />Extra Sauce</td><td width="25%">Cheese Bread:&nbsp; 12"&nbsp; 16"<br />Cinnamon Knots<br />Ranch<br />Marinara</td></tr></tbody></table><p>**<strong>FOOD-ALLERGIC INDIVIDUALS</strong>:&nbsp; Please note that we handle and prepare egg, milk, wheat, shellfish, fish, soy, peanut, tree nut and other potential allergens in our cafes and kitchens.&nbsp; Please inform your server if you have a food allergy and direct questions to a supervisor.&nbsp; For additional information, please visit <a href="http://foodservices.appstate.edu/dining/nutrition-resources">Nutritional Resources</a>.**</p><p><a href="http://www.foodservices.appstate.edu/dining/menus">&lt; back to menus</a></p><p><a href="//www.pinterest.com/pin/create/extension/"></a></p>  </div>



  
